  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study want to proove that the device of watch by  SMS reduced the number of suicidants
      recidivists in six months according to the beginning of its implementation in the group of
      the patients benefiting SMS compared with the group of patients benefiting from the usual
      care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
